<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RHOSP — Complete Architecture & End-to-End Flow</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg-void: #020b18;
    --bg-deep: #041225;
    --bg-panel: #071e38;
    --bg-card: #0a2540;
    --bg-card2: #0d2d4a;
    --accent-primary: #00d4ff;
    --accent-secondary: #0094cc;
    --accent-glow: rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
    --accent-gold: #f0a500;
    --accent-green: #00e676;
    --accent-red: #ff4444;
    --accent-purple: #a78bfa;
    --text-primary: #e8f4fd;
    --text-secondary: #8ab4cc;
    --text-dim: #4a7a9b;
    --border: rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
    --border-bright: rgba(0,212,255,0.5);
    --grid: rgba(0,212,255,0.04);
  }

- { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
background: var(–bg-void);
color: var(–text-primary);
font-family: ‘Inter’, sans-serif;
line-height: 1.6;
overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── GRID BACKGROUND ── */
body::before {
content: ‘’;
position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
background-image:
linear-gradient(var(–grid) 1px, transparent 1px),
linear-gradient(90deg, var(–grid) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 40px 40px;
pointer-events: none;
}

.wrapper { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }

/* ── HERO HEADER ── */
.hero {
text-align: center;
padding: 60px 20px 50px;
position: relative;
}
.hero::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
width: 600px; height: 300px;
background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0,212,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-badge {
display: inline-block;
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
color: var(–accent-primary);
background: rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 5px 18px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero h1 {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px);
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.1;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, var(–accent-primary) 50%, #0094cc 100%);
-webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero-sub {
font-size: 16px; color: var(–text-secondary);
max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px;
font-weight: 300;
}
.hero-tags { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.tag {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 12px;
border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid;
}
.tag-blue  { color: var(–accent-primary);  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3);  background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06); }
.tag-gold  { color: var(–accent-gold);     border-color: rgba(240,165,0,0.3);  background: rgba(240,165,0,0.06); }
.tag-green { color: var(–accent-green);    border-color: rgba(0,230,118,0.3);  background: rgba(0,230,118,0.06); }
.tag-purple{ color: var(–accent-purple);   border-color: rgba(167,139,250,0.3);background: rgba(167,139,250,0.06);}

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
.divider {
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(–accent-secondary), transparent);
margin: 40px 0;
}

/* ── SECTION HEADERS ── */
.section-header {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.section-number {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-primary);
background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 6px;
padding: 4px 10px;
white-space: nowrap;
}
.section-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-primary);
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.section-line {
flex: 1; height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(–border), transparent);
}

/* ── CARDS ── */
.card {
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 24px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
}
.card::before {
content: ‘’; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(–accent-primary), transparent);
}
.card-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-primary);
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: 1px;
margin-bottom: 14px;
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}

/* ── GRID LAYOUTS ── */
.grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
.grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
.grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
@media(max-width:900px){ .grid-2,.grid-3,.grid-4{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
@media(max-width:1100px){ .grid-4{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }

/* ── SERVICE CHIPS ── */
.chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
.chip {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 6px;
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
}
.chip-blue   { color:#00d4ff; background:rgba(0,212,255,0.1);  border:1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.25); }
.chip-green  { color:#00e676; background:rgba(0,230,118,0.1);  border:1px solid rgba(0,230,118,0.25); }
.chip-gold   { color:#f0a500; background:rgba(240,165,0,0.1);  border:1px solid rgba(240,165,0,0.25); }
.chip-purple { color:#a78bfa; background:rgba(167,139,250,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.25);}
.chip-red    { color:#ff6b6b; background:rgba(255,107,107,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.25);}
.chip-teal   { color:#00bcd4; background:rgba(0,188,212,0.1);  border:1px solid rgba(0,188,212,0.25); }
.chip-dot { width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:currentColor; flex-shrink:0; }

/* ── OVERVIEW BOXES ── */
.overview-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
@media(max-width:900px){ .overview-grid{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
.overview-box {
background: var(–bg-panel);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 18px 16px;
text-align: center;
}
.overview-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.overview-label {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 12px; color: var(–text-secondary);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.overview-value {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-primary);
}

/* ── FLOW DIAGRAM ── */
.flow-container {
background: var(–bg-panel);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 30px;
}
.flow-steps {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
gap: 0;
position: relative;
}
.flow-step {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
text-align: center; padding: 16px 12px;
position: relative;
}
.flow-step:not(:last-child)::after {
content: ‘→’;
position: absolute; right: -8px; top: 50%;
transform: translateY(-50%);
color: var(–accent-primary);
font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;
z-index: 2;
}
.step-num {
width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
background: rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
border: 2px solid var(–accent-primary);
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-primary);
margin-bottom: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.step-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.step-name {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-primary);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.step-desc {
font-size: 11px; color: var(–text-secondary);
line-height: 1.4;
}
.step-box {
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 14px 16px;
width: 100%;
}

/* ── VERTICAL FLOW ── */
.vflow { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0; }
.vflow-item {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
width: 100%; max-width: 600px;
}
.vflow-box {
flex: 1;
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 14px 20px;
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
}
.vflow-arrow {
text-align: center;
color: var(–accent-primary);
font-size: 20px;
padding: 4px 0;
width: 100%; max-width: 600px;
}
.vflow-step-num {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-primary);
background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 50%; width: 28px; height: 28px;
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.vflow-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.vflow-text { flex: 1; }
.vflow-name {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-primary);
}
.vflow-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(–text-secondary); }

/* ── COMPARISON TABLE ── */
.compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; }
.compare-table th {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
padding: 14px 18px; text-align: left;
border-bottom: 2px solid var(–border);
}
.compare-table td {
font-size: 13px; padding: 12px 18px;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
vertical-align: top;
}
.compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.compare-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.04); }
.th-rhosp { color: var(–accent-primary); }
.th-ocp   { color: var(–accent-purple); }
.th-feature { color: var(–text-secondary); }
.val-rhosp  { color: #7dd3fc; }
.val-ocp    { color: #c4b5fd; }

/* ── NODE BOXES ── */
.node-box {
background: var(–bg-panel);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 20px;
position: relative;
}
.node-label {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–accent-primary);
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 3px 12px;
display: inline-block;
margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.node-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.node-subtitle {
font-size: 12px; color: var(–text-secondary);
margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.node-services {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
}
.svc-row {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
border-radius: 6px;
padding: 8px 12px;
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
}
.svc-icon { font-size: 14px; }
.svc-name { color: var(–text-primary); flex: 1; }
.svc-badge {
font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 8px;
border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid;
}
.badge-api    { color:#00d4ff; border-color:rgba(0,212,255,0.3); background:rgba(0,212,255,0.08); }
.badge-db     { color:#f0a500; border-color:rgba(240,165,0,0.3);  background:rgba(240,165,0,0.08); }
.badge-mq     { color:#a78bfa; border-color:rgba(167,139,250,0.3);background:rgba(167,139,250,0.08);}
.badge-net    { color:#00e676; border-color:rgba(0,230,118,0.3);  background:rgba(0,230,118,0.08); }
.badge-vm     { color:#ff9800; border-color:rgba(255,152,0,0.3);  background:rgba(255,152,0,0.08); }
.badge-kv     { color:#ef5350; border-color:rgba(239,83,80,0.3);  background:rgba(239,83,80,0.08); }
.badge-ui     { color:#26c6da; border-color:rgba(38,198,218,0.3); background:rgba(38,198,218,0.08);}
.badge-stor   { color:#ffb300; border-color:rgba(255,179,0,0.3);  background:rgba(255,179,0,0.08); }
.badge-sys    { color:#8ab4cc; border-color:rgba(138,180,204,0.3);background:rgba(138,180,204,0.08);}

/* ── WARNING/ALERT BOXES ── */
.alert-box {
border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px;
display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
}
.alert-warn { background: rgba(240,165,0,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(240,165,0,0.3); }
.alert-info { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.25); }
.alert-success { background: rgba(0,230,118,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(0,230,118,0.25); }
.alert-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.alert-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.alert-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(–text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

/* ── DB CLUSTER ── */
.db-cluster {
display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 12px;
margin-top: 14px;
}
@media(max-width:700px){ .db-cluster{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
.db-item {
background: var(–bg-panel);
border: 1px solid rgba(240,165,0,0.2);
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 12px 14px;
text-align: center;
}
.db-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.db-name {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-gold);
}
.db-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(–text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }

/* ── NETWORKING FLOW ── */
.net-flow {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
overflow-x: auto; padding: 10px 0;
}
.net-node {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
text-align: center; min-width: 100px; padding: 10px;
}
.net-node-box {
background: var(–bg-card);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 10px 14px;
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
color: var(–text-primary);
white-space: nowrap;
}
.net-arrow {
color: var(–accent-primary);
font-size: 20px; padding: 0 4px;
white-space: nowrap;
}
.net-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(–text-dim); margin-top: 4px; }

/* ── CONTAINER CARDS ── */
.container-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 12px; }
@media(max-width:800px){ .container-grid{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
.container-card {
background: rgba(167,139,250,0.05);
border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.2);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 14px;
text-align: center;
}
.container-top {
font-size: 10px; color: var(–accent-purple);
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
margin-bottom: 6px;
opacity: 0.7;
}
.container-name {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
color: #c4b5fd;
}
.container-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(–text-dim); margin-top: 4px; }

/* ── HIGHLIGHT BOX ── */
.highlight-box {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.08), rgba(0,148,204,0.04));
border: 1px solid var(–border-bright);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 24px 28px;
text-align: center;
}
.highlight-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–accent-primary);
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.highlight-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(–text-secondary); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
.footer {
text-align: center;
padding: 40px 20px 0;
border-top: 1px solid var(–border);
margin-top: 60px;
}
.footer-text {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 12px; color: var(–text-dim);
}
.footer-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-primary);
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* ── PROBLEM LIST ── */
.problem-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
.problem-item {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
background: rgba(255,68,68,0.06);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.2);
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 10px 14px;
font-size: 13px;
}
.problem-icon { color: #ff6b6b; font-size: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.problem-text { color: var(–text-secondary); }

/* ── TAGLINES ── */
.taglines {
display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px;
padding: 20px 0;
}
.tagline {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–text-dim);
padding: 6px 16px;
border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
border-radius: 20px;
white-space: nowrap;
}

/* ── PLANE BOXES ── */
.planes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
@media(max-width:700px){ .planes{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.plane-box {
border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px;
position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.plane-ctrl {
background: rgba(0,212,255,0.05);
border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
}
.plane-comp {
background: rgba(0,230,118,0.05);
border: 1px solid rgba(0,230,118,0.3);
}
.plane-label {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px;
display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.plane-ctrl .plane-label { color: var(–accent-primary); background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1); }
.plane-comp .plane-label { color: var(–accent-green); background: rgba(0,230,118,0.1); }
.plane-title {
font-family: ‘Rajdhani’, sans-serif;
font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.plane-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(–text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.plane-subtitle {
font-size: 11px; font-style: italic;
padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px;
margin-top: 14px; text-align: center;
}
.plane-ctrl .plane-subtitle { color: var(–accent-primary); background: rgba(0,212,255,0.08); }
.plane-comp .plane-subtitle { color: var(–accent-green); background: rgba(0,230,118,0.08); }

section { margin-bottom: 60px; }

/* ── STORAGE FLOW ── */
.stor-flow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
@media(max-width:700px){ .stor-flow{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ── TLS FLOW ── */
.tls-chain {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
background: var(–bg-panel);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 16px 20px;
overflow-x: auto;
}
.tls-node {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
text-align: center; padding: 8px 14px;
min-width: 90px;
}
.tls-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.tls-name {
font-family: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px; color: var(–text-primary); font-weight: 600;
}
.tls-sub { font-size: 10px; color: var(–text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }
.tls-arrow { color: var(–accent-primary); font-size: 20px; padding: 0 4px; }

/* spacer */
.sp { height: 20px; }
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

  <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">🔴 Red Hat OpenStack Platform</div>
    <h1>RHOSP Complete Architecture<br>& End-to-End Flow</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A deep-dive into the distributed cloud operating system powering enterprise private clouds, telecom environments, and large-scale datacenters worldwide.</p>
    <div class="hero-tags">
      <span class="tag tag-blue">IaaS Platform</span>
      <span class="tag tag-gold">KVM Virtualization</span>
      <span class="tag tag-green">Containerized Control Plane</span>
      <span class="tag tag-purple">Enterprise Private Cloud</span>
      <span class="tag tag-blue">OpenStack</span>
      <span class="tag tag-gold">MariaDB + RabbitMQ</span>
    </div>
  </div>

