  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">📨 RabbitMQ — Internal Message Bus</div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:14px;">RabbitMQ is the async communication backbone. Services don't call each other directly — they publish and consume messages, decoupling API from execution.</p>
